Motion detection with the Raspberry Pi, Python, and OpenCVShell

|--- automate_surveillance.py - Starts server.py on Main server
|--- motion_detection.py - Main motion detection code
|--- conf.json - JSON configuration file
|--- tempimage
|    |--- __init__.py
|    |--- tempimage.py - Temporary writes images to disk

To run the program;

1.run python3 automate_surveillance.py
2.Make sure to run the next command on a virtual environment
3.run python2 motion_detection.py --conf conf.json